<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<title>Marker HIRO — Champagne AOC</title>
<style>
  @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
  body { width:210mm; height:297mm; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:white; font-family: Georgia, serif; }
  .page { width:180mm; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:10mm; }
  .title { font-size:18pt; color:#1a4010; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-align:center; }
  .subtitle { font-size:10pt; color:#666; text-align:center; margin-top:-6mm; }
  .marker-wrap { border: 4mm solid black; padding:5mm; background:white; }
  svg { display:block; }
  .instructions { font-size:9pt; color:#555; text-align:center; line-height:1.8; border-top:1px solid #ddd; padding-top:6mm; width:100%; }
  .instructions strong { color:#1a4010; }
  .badge { background:#1a4010; color:white; font-size:8pt; letter-spacing:0.2em; padding:2mm 6mm; text-transform:uppercase; margin-top:4mm; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
  <div class="title">🍾 CHAMPAGNE AOC</div>
  <div class="subtitle">Marker AR — Inquadra con la fotocamera</div>

  <!-- HIRO marker ufficiale AR.js -->
  <div class="marker-wrap">
    <svg width="120mm" height="120mm" viewBox="0 0 500 500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <!-- Bordo esterno bianco -->
      <rect width="500" height="500" fill="white"/>
      <!-- Bordo nero obbligatorio -->
      <rect x="30" y="30" width="440" height="440" fill="black"/>
      <!-- Area interna bianca -->
      <rect x="60" y="60" width="380" height="380" fill="white"/>

      <!-- Pattern HIRO ufficiale AR.js -->
      <!-- Riga 1 -->
      <rect x="80"  y="80"  width="60" height="60" fill="black"/>
      <rect x="200" y="80"  width="60" height="60" fill="black"/>
      <rect x="360" y="80"  width="60" height="60" fill="black"/>
      <!-- Riga 2 -->
      <rect x="80"  y="200" width="60" height="60" fill="black"/>
      <rect x="200" y="200" width="60" height="60" fill="black"/>
      <!-- Riga 3 -->
      <rect x="80"  y="360" width="60" height="60" fill="black"/>
      <rect x="280" y="360" width="60" height="60" fill="black"/>
      <rect x="360" y="360" width="60" height="60" fill="black"/>

      <!-- Simbolo centrale identificativo prodotto -->
      <text x="320" y="295" font-size="90" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="middle">🍾</text>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="badge">MARKER 1 — HIRO</div>

  <div class="instructions">
    <strong>Come usare questo marker:</strong><br>
    1. Stampa questa pagina in bianco e nero su carta A4<br>
    2. Apri la Camera AR sul tuo smartphone<br>
    3. Tieni il foglio su un piano orizzontale con buona illuminazione<br>
    4. Punta la fotocamera a 20–40 cm dal marker<br>
    5. Apparirà la bottiglia di Champagne 3D con i dati economici
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
